Packages that use lu.uni.geko.common
lu.uni.geko The base package of the main plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver. 
lu.uni.geko.common The base package of the common plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver. 
lu.uni.geko.ext.ifc The base package for an extension that customises GeKo, a generic model weaver, for IFC building models. 
lu.uni.geko.joinpointdetection The base package of the join point detection plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver. 
lu.uni.geko.joinpointdetection.drools The base package of a Drools implementation of the join point detection plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver. 
lu.uni.geko.mapping The base package of the plug-in responsible for resolving a mapping from pointcut elements to advice elements for GeKo, a generic model weaver. 
lu.uni.geko.mmtransformer The base package of the metamodel transformation plug-in used for deriving pointcut and advice metamodels from a base metamodel for GeKo, a generic model weaver. 
lu.uni.geko.weaver The base package of the weaver plug-in for GeKo, a generic model weaver.
